<title>Groong Network: Izvestia: The medics were murdered by racketeers?</title>
<h1>Izvestia: The medics were murdered by racketeers?</h1>
Arthur Martirosyan (<i>martiros@hulaw1.harvard.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Thu, 19 Dec 1996 11:08:13 -0500</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#169">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#169">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#169">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#169">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0170.html">Arthur Martirosyan: "Izvestia: Who was interested in this?"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0168.html">Arthur Martirosyan: "Izvestia: Turkey considers Chechnya part of Russia"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
