<title>Groong Network: Izvestia: Turkey considers Chechnya part of Russia</title>
<h1>Izvestia: Turkey considers Chechnya part of Russia</h1>
Arthur Martirosyan (<i>martiros@hulaw1.harvard.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Thu, 19 Dec 1996 10:27:53 -0500</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#168">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#168">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#168">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#168">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
