<title>Groong Network: DEDICATION OF NEW EMBASSY BUILDING IN OTTAWA</title>
<h1>DEDICATION OF NEW EMBASSY BUILDING IN OTTAWA</h1>
<i>erac@ican.net</i><br>
<i>Wed, 18 Dec 96 17:44:03 PST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#165">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#165">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#165">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#165">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0166.html">Arthur Martirosyan: "Ciller's visit to Moscow"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0164.html">ASBAREZ-ON-LINE: "ASBAREZ-ON-LINE [12-18-96]"</a>
