<title>Groong Network: ANCA: Clinton Nominee for US Ambassador to UN Proponent of Armenian American Issues</title>
<h1>ANCA: Clinton Nominee for US Ambassador to UN Proponent of Armenian American Issues</h1>
ANCA-DC (<i>anca-dc@ix.netcom.com</i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 17 Dec 1996 13:41:27 -0800</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#150">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#150">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#150">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#150">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0151.html">Chavoush@aol.com: "Armenian News 12/17/96"</a>
