          MOUNTAINOUS GHARABAGH<br>
          ---------------------<br>
1. Hrant Bagratian To Work On A Foreign Investments Program In RMK<br>
------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
<p>
     STEPANAKERT ("Azg" daily - Past), 12/14/96  --  As  we  have <br>
already reported, quoting the Past agency, former Prime  Minister <br>
of Armenia Hrant Bagratian was expected to  be  assigned  as  the <br>
Minister of Finance or Economy of the RMK. <br>
     The same  sources  reported  that  this  assignment  is  not <br>
realistic yet, but that Bagratian is now seriously  busy  on  the <br>
development of a foreign investments  program,  coordinated  with <br>
the RMK government. <br>
<!-- body="end" -->
