<p>
Topics:<br>
=================================================================<br>
          MOUNTAINOUS GHARABAGH<br>
          ---------------------<br>
1. Hrant Bagratian To Work On A Foreign Investments Program In RMK<br>
<p>
          POLITICS<br>
          --------<br>
2. ROA Prime Minister Returned From London<br>
   Plachido Domingo Is Invited To Held A Concert In Yerevan<br>
3. Prime Minister Met With The Representatives Of ARFD<br>
<p>
          ENERGY<br>
          ------<br>
4. Cheaper Night Tariffs For Electric Power To Be Installed<br>
