<title>Groong Network: VOA/Turkey/Military</title>
<h1>VOA/Turkey/Military</h1>
Kevork K. Oskanian (<i>100436.3410@compuserve.com</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 11 Dec 96 12:47:26 PST</i>
<p>
<ul>
