CATHOLICOS VISITS POPE JOHN PAUL II<br>
<p>
ISTANBUL ("Lraper" 7 Dec 96) - His Holiness Catholicos Karekin I of All <br>
Armenians will pay an official ecumenical visit His Holiness Pope John <br>
Paull II between 10 and 14 December 1996. The Catholicos will be <br>
accompanied by His Beatitude Patriarch Karekin II of Constantinople and <br>
His Beatitude Torkom II of Jerusalem. The entourage will also include <br>
quite a few archbishops from Armenia and the Diaspora.<br>
<p>
This is the first pontifical summit between the prelates of the Roman <br>
Catholic and Armenian churches since 1970.<br>
<!-- body="end" -->
