ISTANBUL ARMENIAN EDITOR LAID TO REST<br>
<p>
ISTANBUL ("Lraper" 7 Dec 1996)- The editor-in-chief of the Istanbul <br>
Armenian daily "Jamanak," Mr Ara Kochunian was laid to rest this <br>
afternoon in the Balikli Armenian National Cemetery.<br>
<p>
The funeral services took place at 14.00 hours at the Surp Astvadzadzin <br>
Patriarchal Cathedral in Kumkapi, presided over by His Beatitude Karekin <br>
II, Armenian Patriarch of Istanbul.<br>
