<title>Groong Network: Catholicos to meet Pope</title>
<h1>Catholicos to meet Pope</h1>
<i>H.TCHILINGIRIAN@lse.ac.uk</i><br>
<i>Sun, 8 Dec 96 9:52:36 PST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#58">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#58">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#58">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#58">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
