<!-- body="start" -->
The Central California Chapter of the Armenian National Committee will<br>
sponsor a panel discussion on the elections in Armenia on Sunday, December 15<br>
at 1:30 PM in the Armenian Community School of Fresno on 1940 N. Fresno St.<br>
<p>
The panel will consist of Osheen Keshishian, editor and publisher of The<br>
Armenian Observer, Ara Khatchatourian, Editor of the English section of<br>
Asbarez and Serge Samoniantz, editor of the California Courier.  The panel<br>
moderator will be Professor Levon Marashlian.<br>
<p>
The public is invited to attend.  The admission is free.  For further<br>
information, call 486-1918.<br>
