<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Azerbaijan: OMRI - 31DEC96 - ANOTHER FRENCH COMPANY TO PARTICIPATE IN AZ</title>
<h1>OMRI - 31DEC96 - ANOTHER FRENCH COMPANY TO PARTICIPATE IN AZ</h1>
<i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Mon, 06 Jan 97 14:33:54 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#61">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#61">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#61">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#61">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0062.html">eurasia@sorosny.org: "OMRI - 3JAN97 - AZERBAIJANI PRESIDENT ON 1996"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0060.html">fsu@mail.sorosny.org: "Interfax 30Dec96 Azeri President Favors CIS Cooperation"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
