<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0061.html">eurasia@sorosny.org: "OMRI - 31DEC96 - ANOTHER FRENCH COMPANY TO PARTICIPATE IN AZ"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0059.html">fsu@mail.sorosny.org: "OMRI - 19DEC96 - RUSSIA UPSET OVER ADAMS/KHACHUKAEV MEETING"</a>
