<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Azerbaijan: OMRI - 19DEC96 - RUSSIA UPSET OVER ADAMS/KHACHUKAEV MEETING</title>
<h1>OMRI - 19DEC96 - RUSSIA UPSET OVER ADAMS/KHACHUKAEV MEETING</h1>
<i>fsu@mail.sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Thu, 19 Dec 96 13:00:35 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#58">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#58">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#58">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#58">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0059.html">fsu@mail.sorosny.org: "OMRI - 19DEC96 - RUSSIA UPSET OVER ADAMS/KHACHUKAEV MEETING"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0057.html">fsu@mail.sorosny.org: "OMRI - 18DEC96 - FREEDOM HOUSE REPORT NOTES LACK OF HUMAN RI"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
