<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Azerbaijan: OMRI 26Nov96 Rasi-Zade Confirmed as Azeri Prime Minister</title>
<h1>OMRI 26Nov96 Rasi-Zade Confirmed as Azeri Prime Minister</h1>
<i>arichter@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Wed, 27 Nov 96 17:21:08 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#47">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#47">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#47">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#47">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
