<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Azerbaijan: OMRI - 19Nov96 - Clinton Praises Azerbaijan's Stance on CFE</title>
<h1>OMRI - 19Nov96 - Clinton Praises Azerbaijan's Stance on CFE</h1>
<i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Tue, 19 Nov 96 10:57:52 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#43">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#43">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#43">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#43">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
