<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Azerbaijan: OMRI--Oct 29 --RUSSIA SLAMS PLANNED NK PRESIDENTIAL ELECTION</title>
<h1>OMRI--Oct 29 --RUSSIA SLAMS PLANNED NK PRESIDENTIAL ELECTION</h1>
<i>arichter@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Tue, 29 Oct 96 11:34:50 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#33">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#33">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#33">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#33">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0034.html">arichter@sorosny.org: "OMRI--Oct 30 --KARABAKH LEADER SAYS ELECTION WILL BE HELD"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0032.html">arichter@sorosny.org: "OMRI--23 Oct 1996--KARABAKH ELECTION RUMPUS"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
