<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Azerbaijan: OMRI--30 August 1996--CONFUSION OVER GERMAN STANCE</title>
<h1>OMRI--30 August 1996--CONFUSION OVER GERMAN STANCE</h1>
<i>eurasia@mail.sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Fri, 30 Aug 96 10:09:02 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#6">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#6">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#6">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#6">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0007.html">tlankina@sorosny.org: "OMRI--3 September 96--IRREDENTIST CAMPAIGN AMONG AZERIS IN I"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0005.html">tlankina@sorosny.org: "OMRI--28 August 96--AZERBAIJAN CREATES ANTI-NARCOTICS COMMIS"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
