<title>Human Rights Center of Azerbaijan: Statistics on IDP</title>
<h1>Statistics on IDP</h1>
<i>agalietti@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Thu, 15 Aug 96 17:01:40 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#9">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#9">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#9">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#9">[ author ]</a>
