<title>Human Rights Center of Azerbaijan: List of Political Prisoners in Azerbaijan</title>
<h1>List of Political Prisoners in Azerbaijan</h1>
Anthony Galietti (<i>agaliett</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 16 Aug 96 09:58:05 EDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#18">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#18">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#18">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#18">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0017.html">Anthony Galietti: "Review of Political Arrests and Trials in Azerbaijan"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
</ul>
<!-- body="start" -->
