              HUMAN RIGHTS CENTER OF AZERBAIJAN                <br>
    150-9, Bashir Safaroglu Street, 370000 Baku, Azerbaijan    <br>
 Tel+994-12-947550, fax 987555, e-mail: eldar@hrcenter.baku.az <br>
<br>
<p>
                       LIST OF PRISONERS,<br>
         arrested in Azerbaijan on political accusation<br>
                       (to February 29'96)<br>
-----------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Surname, Name, Patronimic  Date  of  Term,  Permanent  Political<br>
   of arrested person       arrest   years  address    membership<br>
