Agayev Natiq (?)           13.09.94    ?    Baku        AM   (s)<br>
Agayev Natiq Hasanaga      Mar.1995   14    Baku?       OPON (m)<br>
Agayev Nazim Asgar         12.01.94    ?    NAR         AXCP (m)<br>
Agayev Rafiq               Aug.1995    ?    Baku        AM   (s)<br>
Ahmedov Aladdin            Aut.1994   11    Ganja       NK   (m)<br>
Ahmedov Anar Tofiq         Mar.1995   11    ?           OPON (m)<br>
Ahmedov Bahadur (??)       06.10.93    ?    Ordubad     AXCP (s)<br>
Ahmedov Chapay             Aut.1994    ?    Ganja       SH   (s)<br>
Ahmedov E.                 Mar.1995   13    Qazax       OPON (m)<br>
Ahmedov Islam              Mar.1995    3    ?           OPON (m)<br>
Ahmedov M.                 Mar.1995   13    Qazax       OPON (m)<br>
Ahmedov Mirintizam (??)    Aut.1993    ?    Baku        AXCP (m)<br>
Ahmedov Namiq              Aut.1993   13    Qubadli     AXCP (m)<br>
Ahmedov V.                 Aut.1994?   ?    ?           SH   (s)<br>
Akberov Israfil Isa        Sep.1994   13    Sharur      AXCP (m)<br>
Akberov Izzet              Aut.1993    ?    NAR         AXCP (m)<br>
Akberov Kamran Qurban      Sep.1993    ?    Lenkaran    AH   (s)<br>
Akberov Nadir Abdulla      17.03.95   14    Baku        OPON (m)<br>
Akberov Tavakkul           Mar.1995   14    Baku        OPON (m)<br>
Alekberov Asim Niftali     Mar.1995   12    Qazax       OPON (m)<br>
Alekberov Eduard Niyaz     Aut.1994    8    Baku        SH   (s)<br>
Alekberov Mammed Jalal     Mar.1995    ?    Ganja       SH   (s)<br>
Alirzayev Aqil Kommunist   Mar.1995    ?    Qazax       OPON (s)<br>
Alirzayev Maqsad Alirza    Mar.1995    ?    Qazax       OPON (s)<br>
Alishov Rizvan Rushan      Sep.1994    5    Baku        AH,RQ(s)<br>
Aliyev Ahmed Baba          01.10.95    ?    Baku        AM   (s)<br>
Aliyev Ali                 14.03.95    ?    Baku        OPON (m)<br>
Aliyev Bayali Khanali      01.10.95    ?    Baku        AM   (s)<br>
Aliyev Elchin Qaraoglan    Aut.1995  death  Baku        OPON (m)<br>
