Notes:<br>
  (?)  - motives of arrest are not clear or lack of information<br>
  (??) - probably, released<br>
  m.   - member<br>
  s.   - supporter<br>
  ADP  - Azerbaijan Democratic Prty<br>
  AEP  - Labour Party of Azerbaijan<br>
  AH   - leader of Talish separatists Alakram Hummatov<br>
  AM   - ex-President Ayaz Mutallibov<br>
  AMDP - Azerb. National Democratic Party "Boz Qurd"("Gray Wolf")<br>
  ASDP - Social-democratic Party of Azerbaijan<br>
  AXBP - Party of Egality of Azerbaijani Peoples<br>
  AXCP - Party of Popular Front of Azerbaijan<br>
  ChTP - Party of "Chagdash Turan" ("Modern Turan")<br>
  LND  - Legzin National Movement "Sadval" ("Unity")<br>
  ME   - Mammed Emin Rasulzade Student Organization<br>
  MP   - Party of "Musavat" ("Equality")<br>
  NAR  - Makhchivan Autonomous Republic of Azerbaijan<br>
  NK   - Charitable Committee of "Nidjat" ("Salvation")<br>
  OPON - Special Unit of Police<br>
  RQ   - ex-Minister of Defense Rahim Qaziyev<br>
  SH   - ex-Premier Suret Huseynov<br>
  XM   - Society in name of Xudu Mammedov<br>
  YAIC - Islamic Society of "Yeni Azeri" ("New Azeri")<br>
<p>
The form of full name of Azeris is (1st name) (Patronimic)+ oglu<br>
(Surname), for example: Nariman Yaman oglu Yahyayev.<br>
